00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:07.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
in a world where love has become a word we use too readily at the end of letters

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:12.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
