00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:35.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
He got with a girl, the next day, that didn't mind him sucking her face.

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:38.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
I found out. I went to the park where he played basketball with his friends.

00:11:38.000 --> 00:11:42.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
