00:31:33.000 --> 00:31:38.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
So I've been learning from the elders who come before me seeking peace from the unanswered American dream

00:31:38.000 --> 00:31:46.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
like the mother of a Filipino postal worker whose son was shot nine times in broad American daylight, so I ask why?

00:31:46.000 --> 00:31:50.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
