00:35:11.000 --> 00:35:15.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
does not mean to forget all the parts of me that is woman, that is soft,

00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:19.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
