00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:24.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
To become the day, that I can embrace my femininity, will be the day I have stepped

00:35:24.000 --> 00:35:26.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
into my true masculinity.

00:35:26.000 --> 00:35:32.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
