00:35:45.000 --> 00:35:47.790 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
Sometimes, it is the only time I can be put to sleep.

00:35:49.000 --> 00:35:55.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
